Requires:
mutt
w3m
isync --> /usr/local/bin/mbsync
bitwarden-cli (bw) --> /usr/local/bin/bw
goimapnotify (https://gitlab.com/shackra/goimapnotify) --> /usr/local/bin/goimapnotify

    $ sudo loginctl enable-linger <username>
    $ systemctl --user enable --now mbsync@posteo
    $ systemctl --user enable --now goimapnotify@posteo.service
